{"tid":773110,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★突發！受醜聞影響　大圍至紅磡段通車無期","createTime":"2018-08-09T09:22:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-09T09:36:27.000Z","uid":19454,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"6720f80b55ecac3aa6c034321bfa1f1c20faa7ad","tid":773110,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T09:22:17.000Z","msg":"港鐵沙中線醜聞不斷，連通車日期及造價也可能受影響。據港鐵今日（9日）最新說法，沙中線大圍至紅磡段的目標完工日期需等待紅磡站月台層的相關核實和安全測試才可決定，與早前所指2019年中完工有明顯出入，亦即意味大圍至紅磡段通車無期。<br />\n另外，沙中線造價最新造價估算原本已增至971億元，業績報告顯示，紅磡站月台的核實或安全測試所引致的任何重大不利後果均可影響最新造價估算。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/220797/沙中線-受醜聞影響-大圍至紅磡段通車無期-造價或增\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F220797%2F%E6%B2%99%E4%B8%AD%E7%B7%9A-%E5%8F%97%E9%86%9C%E8%81%9E%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF-%E5%A4%A7%E5%9C%8D%E8%87%B3%E7%B4%85%E7%A3%A1%E6%AE%B5%E9%80%9A%E8%BB%8A%E7%84%A1%E6%9C%9F-%E9%80%A0%E5%83%B9%E6%88%96%E5%A2%9E&d=4HARd12Fs2HlhsTp1kULoRv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=47262cc3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/220797/沙中線-受醜聞影響-大圍至紅磡段通車無期-造價或增</a>"},{"pid":"6e38d2f9f679bcb191285d602f913ee49bac9f6c","tid":773110,"uid":103759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T09:23:06.000Z","msg":"好野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中國好波 利害了 我的國"},{"pid":"687d7abdfda1a9a08369e0ef1a4ceb46994bf0f5","tid":773110,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T09:23:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"453303d28fefed0accfffae1d150fd26d155040e","tid":773110